<div class="wrapper">
  <div id="services" class="row  white center" >
    <div class="col s12">
      <h4 class="header center">What We do</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="row center container">
      <div class="col s12 m4 l-card">
        <div class="card-panel color-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <%= image_tag "design.gif", class: "l-card-image" %>
          </div>
          <span class="grey-text darken-3">
            You have only one chance to make
            a great impression.
            <br>
            How your platform looks like is one of
            the main reason why a customer will
            stay or leave.
          </span>
          <div class="card-action one">
            <button data-target="modal1" class="btn modal-trigger btn waves-effect waves-light">Learn More..</button>

            <div id="modal1" class="modal">
              <div class="modal-content">
                <h4>Modal Header</h4>
                <p>A bunch of text</p>
              </div>
              <div class="modal-footer">
                <a href="#!" class=" modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">Agree</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m4 c-card">
        <div class="card-panel color-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <%= image_tag "code.gif", class: "l-card-image" %>
          </div>
          <span class="deep-orange-text lighten-5">
            As Ruby on Rails Developer we can
            Develop complex platform
            in a fast and efficient way.
            <br>
            For any startup
            time is important.
            Therefore we choose to work with Ruby.
          </span>
          <div class="card-action two">
            <a class="btn waves-effect waves-light" href="#">Learn More..</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m4 r-card">
        <div class="card-panel color-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <%= image_tag "launch.gif", class: "l-card-image" %>
          </div>
          <span class="blue-grey-text darken-4">
            Once the Design is done,
            Your website created,
            Time to get some customers.
            <br>
            We provide an amazing analytics system for your online marketing tools such as (SEO/SEM).
            
          </span>
          <div class="card-action three">
            <a class="btn waves-effect waves-light" href="#">Learn More..</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
